  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This standard defines a multi-asset basket token that extends [ERC-20](./eip-20.md). A basket holds a set of [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) constituent tokens at configurable target weights. The basket contract itself is the share token: holders of the basket's [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) supply have a proportional claim on its underlying reserves. A designated owner, identified via [ERC-173](./eip-173.md), has authority to rebalance the basket's composition.",
  "title": "Basket Token"
